      <title>法国相对于德国的风险溢价达到 2012 年以来的最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/france-s-risk-premium-over-germany-closes-at-highest-since-2012</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们越来越担心，争夺法国即将到来的立法选举的政党可能会进一步导致公共财政膨胀，投资者对法国债券的持有要求比对更安全的德国债券的持有要求高出十多年来的最大溢价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/france-s-risk-premium-over-germany-closes-at-highest-since-2012</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 16:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国即将限制对华芯片和人工智能技术的投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/us-moves-closer-to-restricting-outbound-investment-in-china-for-chips-ai-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府提出限制美国个人和企业对华投资的计划，重点是遏制北京在半导体、量子计算和人工智能领域取得进展的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/us-moves-closer-to-restricting-outbound-investment-in-china-for-chips-ai-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度教徒被判犯有瑞士别墅奴役罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/hindujas-found-guilty-of-exploitation-of-servants-at-swiss-villa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁欣杜贾家族的四名成员因在其日内瓦豪华别墅中非法剥削低薪仆人而被判有罪，这一判决对印度最富有和最具影响力的家族之一的瑞士分支来说是毁灭性的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/hindujas-found-guilty-of-exploitation-of-servants-at-swiss-villa</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 15:38:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国 1020 亿美元预算获得立法者初步批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/thailand-s-102-billion-budget-gets-initial-nod-from-lawmakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国下议院投票通过了下一财年 1020 亿美元的预算，旨在增加政府支出，推动东南亚第二大经济体的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/thailand-s-102-billion-budget-gets-initial-nod-from-lawmakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 15:18:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
